      "date": "2017-09-15 08:39:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nAndreas, it was Centos 6.5:\n\n[root@panda-testbox ~]# rpm -qi glibc-devel\nName        : glibc-devel                  Relocations: (not relocatable)\nVersion     : 2.12                              Vendor: CentOS\nRelease     : 1.166.el6_7.7                 Build Date: Tue 16 Feb 2016 10:38:37 PM MSK",
